.SH NAME
vmw_cmdbuf_work_func \- The deferred work function that handles command buffer errors.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" vmw_cmdbuf_work_func
.BI "(struct work_struct *work "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "work" 12
The work func closure argument.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Restarting the command buffer context after an error requires process
context, so it is deferred to this work function.
